  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e98051a6c4ccd6a4a90a180c0343c7b9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Hints_Spinner
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  speaker: []
  dialogue:
  - This is the reel in game. Your goal here is to keep the fish inside of the large
    green zone, which you control.
  - Hold [Left Click / RT] to move the large green zone counter clockwise. Do nothing
    to let it move clockwise.
  - As you progress the grey outline around the spinner will show you how much you
    have completed or how close you are to fail.
  - 'If it goes all the way back down it you will loose the mini game and the fish. '
  - When you first start up though don't worry you'll have some grace time.
  audioclip: []
